Detailed Description

FdoINetworkReachingNodesCommand subclasses from FdoINetworkCommand and is the main interface that defines the FDO reaching nodes analysis feature. An instance can be created through the FdoIConnection::CreateCommand method. Not all FDO providers will support this command. The FdoICommandCapability should be used to verify if a given provider support this command.
